node.text: Which tip do you agree with the most?

node.title: Warren Buffet's Top Tips for Investing in the Stock Market

node.text:
“The best time to plant a tree was 20 years ago. The second best time is now.”

Everyone wishes they would have started sooner when they finally make the jump into investing. 

Start now, your future self will thank you.
Get money, buy assets, & act broke 💯
Start thinking in 10 year terms, not 10 day terms!

Good financial decisions = Good financial future.

Bad financial decisions = Bad financial future. 

The choice is yours to make. 💯
Reminder: new habits = new outcomes. You can’t get different outcomes with the same exact habits.
Bad money habits leads to more problems than just being broke..

node.text: “The best time to plant a tree was 20 years ago. The second best time is now.”
The more you learn about money, the harder it gets to spend money on things that don’t make you more money.
Let me be clear: I’m after the freedom, NOT the money! Money is just a tool to get there. 🔥

node.text:
The financial position you are in today is based on the financial choices you made in the past. 

The financial position you’ll be in 2030 will be based on the financial choices you make today.
Doesn’t matter how old you are, you’ll always wish you would have started earlier when you start to understand how investing works. Never fails. 😂
